# Category routing

- Primary categories: `simulation`, `data-analysis`, `literature`, `writing`, `course-prep`, `chore`.
- Prefer delegating to `.cursor/agents/<category>.md` when the task matches.
- Put outputs in the matching folder; shared libraries go in `shared/`.
- Cloud agents only see this git repo — no laptop-only paths unless documented.
- Keep `.cursor/environment.json` lean. Verify plots with `python3 data-analysis/example_scientific_plot.py`.
